column5: Santa came early this year, well actually it was Brian and dropped off a real nice variety of jig heads, from micro size to laker killers.  I'll be trying them out as soon as La Nina leaves town and we can get some ice for a change.  Thanks Brian, much appreciated.
Those all look good but those 2 on the bottom many I need some of those!  Cheers!
Oh crap,,,,,,,,,,,,,, I think I gave you the wrong package. Those are fish CATCHING bugs. They were to go to Terry. DANG LOL Karma my friend Karma Thanks again  See ya on the hard water. Soon I hope
now santa just needs to actually deliver some ice this year
Without snow to screw it all up.
